---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'February 28, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Spirit Media Publishing"
  description="Spirit Media Publishing's terms of service — the rules and guidelines that govern use of our website and services."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  </Fragment>
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12 border-b border-stone-200 pb-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-red">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-soft sm:text-4xl">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-7 text-stone-600">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            By accessing or using the Spirit Media Publishing website (the "Site"), you agree to be
            bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use
            the Site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">2. Use of the site</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes. You must not:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 pl-4">
            <li>Use the Site in any way that violates applicable local, national, or international law.</li>
            <li>
              Transmit any unsolicited or unauthorised advertising or promotional material (spam).
            </li>
            <li>
              Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Site or its related systems.
            </li>
            <li>
              Reproduce, duplicate, or exploit any part of the Site for commercial purposes without
              our express written permission.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">3. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            All content on this Site — including text, images, logos, and design — is the property
            of Spirit Media Publishing or its content suppliers and is protected by copyright and
            intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce or redistribute content without prior
            written consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">4. Third-party links</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The Site may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for
            convenience only. We have no control over the content of those sites and accept no
            responsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from your use of them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">5. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The Site is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. To the fullest extent
            permitted by law, Spirit Media Publishing makes no warranties, express or implied,
            regarding the Site's operation, availability, or the accuracy of its content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Spirit Media Publishing shall not be liable for
            any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of, or
            inability to use, the Site or its content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">7. Privacy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Your use of the Site is also governed by our{' '}
            <a href="/privacy" class="text-red hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>, which is
            incorporated into these Terms by reference.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">8. Changes to these terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this
            page with a revised "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after any changes
            constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">9. Governing law</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with applicable law. Any
            disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Site shall be subject to the
            exclusive jurisdiction of the relevant courts.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-soft">10. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Questions about these Terms should be directed to{' '}
            <a href="mailto:info@spiritmedia.us" class="text-red hover:underline">
              info@spiritmedia.us
            </a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
